name: 甘奈
text:
はぁ、テレビって緊張するね……！
ちょっと疲れちゃったかも
trans:
Phew... Who would've thought appearing on TV could 
be so nerve-wracking...! I'm feeling a bit burnt out...

name: プロデューサー
trans: Great work out there! You did really well.

name: 甘奈
text:
う～ん、そうかな？
甘奈はあんまりうまくできなかった感じがするよ？
trans:
Hmm～ You really think so? 
I feel like I didn't do that well though...?

name: プロデューサー
text:
そんなことない
ちゃんとやれていたさ
trans: Come on, you did really well out there.

name: 甘奈
text:
そうかな～、やっぱりカメラがあると
いつもレッスンしてる時とは違う感じがするよ～
trans:
Are you really sure about that～? 
With cameras everywhere, it felt so different from
how it is during lessons～

name: 甘奈
text: いつもみたいに、ステップできなかったもん
trans:
Because of that, I wasn't really able to execute 
some steps as properly as I usually do.

name: プロデューサー
text: でも、しっかりと分析ができていて偉いぞ！
trans:
But still, you managed to come to a conclusion after 
a thorough personal analysis. That's already 
impressive!

name: 甘奈
text: えへへ、そう言ってくれると嬉しいかな
trans:
Ehehe, hearing those words from you really lifts my 
spirits!

name: プロデューサー
text: よし、今日できなかったところをしっかり克服しよう
trans:
Alright! Let's reflect on today's mistakes and aim 
to do even better next time.

name: 甘奈
text:
だね！
ありがとうプロデューサーさん☆
trans:
Right on!
Thank you so much, Producer-san☆
